ZH: 我们可以一起来打篮球。
EN: We can play basketball together.

ZH: 你想要我来帮助你吗？
EN: Do you want me to help you?

ZH: 明天我来接你去机场。
EN: I will come pick you up tomorrow to go to the airport.

ZH: 你可以来我们家吃晚饭。
EN: You can come to our house for dinner.

ZH: 这个星期日你要来参加我的生日派对吗？
EN: Will you come to my birthday party this Sunday?

ZH: 他们正在商量明天要不要来看电影。
EN: They are discussing whether to come watch a movie tomorrow.

ZH: 请你来看看这个新的展览。
EN: Please come take a look at this new exhibition.

ZH: 我们需要你来决定这个问题。
EN: We need you to come and make a decision on this issue.

ZH: 孩子们喜欢叔叔每次来家里玩。
EN: The kids like it when their uncle comes to play at our house.

ZH: 我们会来走一走你们新搬来的邻居。
EN: We will come and visit your new neighbors.

ZH: 我会来帮你解决这个难题。
EN: I will come help you solve this difficult problem.

ZH: 他们决定这个周末来参观博物馆。
EN: They decided to come visit the museum this weekend.

ZH: 请你明天来见我面试。
EN: Please come for an interview with me tomorrow.

ZH: 你可以来我办公室拿这份文件。
EN: You can come to my office to pick up this document.

ZH: 我们约定好明天下午来商量这个计划。
EN: We agreed to come discuss this plan tomorrow afternoon.

ZH: 你什么时候来访我们这里？
EN: When will you come visit us here?

ZH: 她常常来看我们这个周末。
EN: She often comes to visit us on weekends.

ZH: 他拒绝来参加这个聚会。
EN: He refused to come to the party.

ZH: 我今天忙，不能来帮你。
EN: I am busy today and cannot come help you.

ZH: 你可以明天再来打电话给我。
EN: You can call me again tomorrow.
